org.finra.herd.tools.common.databridge

Class DataBridgeController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.finra.herd.tools.common.databridge.DataBridgeController
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DownloaderController, UploaderController

    public abstract class DataBridgeController
extends Object
    A base class for the uploader and downloader controller. This class is abstract since it is not an actual controller, but just a help class that provides common base functionality that should be used by an extending class.

      • getStorageNameFromManifest

        protected String getStorageNameFromManifest(DataBridgeBaseManifestDto manifest)
        Gets the storage name from a databridge manifest. Defaults to S3 managed storage when manifest does not specify a storage name. The storage name is whitespace trimmed.
